# Java API test files

When adding or editing tests in `*Test.java` or `*ApiTest.java`:

- Use `given().when().then()` and assert status with `.statusCode(...)`.
- For each happy-path test, add at least one negative case (400, 404, or invalid input) where relevant.
- Keep the same naming and structure as existing tests in the file (e.g. `shouldReturn200_when...`, `shouldReturn404_when...`).
